    "title": "About CSS Engineers",
    "paragraphs": [
      "CSS ENGINEERS PRIVATE LIMITED is a leading transmission line survey, geotechnical, and foundation engineering company based in Chakia, Chandauli, Uttar Pradesh, India. With over 12 years of experience, we deliver precise surveys and robust engineering solutions for India's power infrastructure.",
      "Our team combines advanced surveying technologies with deep field expertise to provide accurate route alignment, detailed surveys, and robust geotechnical assessments. We have successfully completed 17+ major transmission line projects across multiple states.",
